## Letak ##

Very tiny (<1kb not gzip) static maps.

### Install
	
	bower install --save letak

### Usage ###

    	Letak('idOftheDiv', {
			lat: 60.390401,
			lng: 5.328541,
			width: 8, // in tiles
			height: 4, // in tiles
			zoom: 8,
			pin: true,
			offset: [-2, 0], // in tiles
			layers:[{
				urlTemplate: 'http://a.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png',
				opacity: 1
			},{
				urlTemplate: 'http://media.stv.stormgeo.com/tile/{z}/{x}/{y}/201411161015/000101010000/?layers=radar&culture=nb-NO',
				opacity:1
			}]
	});

### Build ###

	gulp build